title: Lemley and Rochard combine for shutout in No. 8 Virginia Tech's 5-0 win over Evansville - VT hokiesports.com
content: Lemley and Rochard combine for shutout in No. 8 Virginia Tech's 5-0 win over Evansville  VT hokiesports.com
description: TUSCALOOSA, Ala.  -- Freshman Emma Lemley and senior Keely Rochard combined to toss a shutout on Sunday as the No. 8 Virginia Tech Hokies blanked the Evansville Purple Aces 5-0.
